2.2 筛选出除夕夜（2024年2月9日）、清明节（2024年4月5日）两日PM2.5的数据

# 除夕夜
d_pm2.5_2.9 <- d_pm2.5 %>%
  filter(date == "20240209")
# 清明节
d_pm2.5_4.5 <- d_pm2.5 %>%
  filter(date == "20240405")

# 除夕夜

2 作图对比2024年1月1日-4月6日，厦门、北京两市PM2.5全市均值的时间序列

2.1 分别筛选出，厦门和北京的数据

d_xiamen <- d_pm2.5 %>%
  filter(city == "厦门") 
d_beijing <- d_pm2.5 %>%
  filter(city == "北京")

2.2 作图分析pm2.5的逐日变化趋势

p_xiamen <- d_xiamen %>%
  mutate(date = ymd(date)) %>% # 将date转化为日期格式
  ggplot(aes(date,value)
        )+
  theme_classic()+
  geom_point(color = "grey") +
  stat_summary(geom = "line",fun = "mean",color = "red")+
  scale_x_date(date_labels = "%m/%d", breaks = "1 month")+ 
  labs(x = "Date", y = "PM2.5",title = "厦门市2024年1-4月PM2.5变化")+
  theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 15,
                                  hjust = 0.5,
                                  vjust = 0.5))+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(0,300))

2.3 按照每日计算均值

d_xiamen_mean <- d_xiamen %>%
    mutate(date = ymd(date),
           year = year(date),
           month = month(date),
           day = day(date)) %>%
    group_by(year,month,day) %>%
    summarise(mean_pm2.5 = mean(value,na.rm = T)) %>%
    mutate(year_month_day = ymd(paste(year,month,day)))
## `summarise()` has grouped output by 'year', 'month'. You can override using the
## `.groups` argument.
d_xiamen_mean %>%
    ggplot(aes(year_month_day,mean_pm2.5)) +
    geom_line(color = "red",width = 1)
## Warning in geom_line(color = "red", width = 1): Ignoring unknown parameters:
## `width`

厦门pm2.5随时间序列分析结果

# 转化为ts格式

library(zoo)
## 
## 载入程辑包：'zoo'
## The following objects are masked from 'package:base':
## 
##     as.Date, as.Date.numeric
d_ts_xiamen <- ts(d_xiamen_mean$mean_pm2.5,
                  start = as.yearmon(d_xiamen_mean$year_month_day),freq = 12)
class(d_ts_xiamen)
## [1] "ts"
plot(decompose(d_ts_xiamen))

ggsave(filename = "ts_xiamen.png",height = 10,width = 15,dpi = 600)
